{"audioUrl": "", "duration": 3198.998, "paragraphs": [{"id": "p1", "sentences": [{"id": "p1s1", "text": "Mon voyage au marché local commence toujours par le doux parfum des fraises fraîches.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mon ", "start": 0.0, "end": 0.221}, {"text": "voyage ", "start": 0.267, "end": 0.627}, {"text": "au ", "start": 0.65, "end": 0.697}, {"text": "marché ", "start": 0.755, "end": 0.998}, {"text": "local ", "start": 1.033, "end": 1.405}, {"text": "commence ", "start": 1.474, "end": 1.765}, {"text": "toujours ", "start": 1.788, "end": 2.183}, {"text": "par ", "start": 2.218, "end": 2.345}, {"text": "le ", "start": 2.38, "end": 2.473}, {"text": "doux ", "start": 2.589, "end": 2.798}, {"text": "parfum ", "start": 2.833, "end": 3.204}, {"text": "des ", "start": 3.262, "end": 3.355}, {"text": "fraises ", "start": 3.379, "end": 3.692}, {"text": "fraîches.", "start": 3.75, "end": 4.354}]}, {"id": "p1s2", "text": "Tôt le samedi matin, les étals regorgent de couleurs éclatantes et de visages amicaux.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Tôt ", "start": 4.946, "end": 5.143}, {"text": "le ", "start": 5.166, "end": 5.248}, {"text": "samedi ", "start": 5.306, "end": 5.573}, {"text": "matin, ", "start": 5.631, "end": 6.235}, {"text": "les ", "start": 6.444, "end": 6.664}, {"text": "étals ", "start": 6.734, "end": 7.07}, {"text": "regorgent ", "start": 7.117, "end": 7.546}, {"text": "de ", "start": 7.593, "end": 7.651}, {"text": "couleurs ", "start": 7.697, "end": 7.999}, {"text": "éclatantes ", "start": 8.034, "end": 8.766}, {"text": "et ", "start": 8.824, "end": 8.94}, {"text": "de ", "start": 8.963, "end": 9.033}, {"text": "visages ", "start": 9.079, "end": 9.52}, {"text": "amicaux.", "start": 9.59, "end": 10.321}]}, {"id": "p1s3", "text": "J'adore parcourir la sélection variée de légumes bio et de fromages artisanaux.", "boundaries": [{"text": "J'adore ", "start": 10.913, "end": 11.355}, {"text": "parcourir ", "start": 11.378, "end": 11.842}, {"text": "la ", "start": 11.9, "en